Hello all,

We will be having 3 vs. 3 half-court games as part of the basketball
freshie Schroeter (both boys and girls).

*No. of members in a team: 4 (ALL FRESHIES)*
*Duration of the game: 10 minutes split into 2 halves*
*Dates and Time: 17 & 18 September, 5 PM*
*Venue: Institute Basketball Court*

Awards and perks:

1. Gymkhana medals and certificates for the winners
2. Chance to get hands on institute basketball T-shirt
3. Show off your talent to institute team and get noticed
4. Bragging rights!

*Registration procedure* - 1 person from each team should send a mail
consisting of the following team details:

Player 1: Name, Roll No. & Hostel
Player 2: Name, Roll No. & Hostel
Player 3: Name, Roll No. & Hostel
Player 4: Name, Roll No. & Hostel

Send the registrations to sagarsjoshi94@gmail.com before 16th September.

